SUMMARY:Tree Conversations by Felicity Somerset
DESCRIPTION:This Tree Conversations exhibition reflects Felicity Somerset”s passion for trees and how that has led her to make this creative\, expressionist collection of photographic images.  The Leslie Grove Gallery from March 25-April 12. Gallery hours: Wednesday to Sunday 12-5 PM.  Opening reception will take place on Thursday\, March 26\, 6-8 pm. Details at https://www.artistsnetwork.ca/patrons-calendar.
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/tree-conversations-by-felicity-somerset/
LOCATION:Leslie Grove Gallery\, 1158 Queen St E\, Toronto\, ON M4M 1L2\, Canada\, Old Toronto\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M4M 1L2
CATEGORIES:Art & Design,Exhibitions
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://nowtoronto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/tree-conversations-by-felicity-somerset.png
END:VEVENT
