SUMMARY:Joe Wunderle
DESCRIPTION:Nashville TN -Joe Wunderle Is a songwriter’s songwriter. He has carved place in the country music and folk worlds as a modern lyricist – gathering stories and songs from the hard miles he’s made and people he has met from the far corners of the world.   \nWith a deep dedication the craft\, Wunderle has toured extensively throughout the United States\, Canada\, and Europe and has released five studio albums as of 2026 with his latest release being the album\, “Here to Stay” \nHis music can be described best as folk storytelling with classic country influences. For fans of: John Prine\, Woody Guthrie\, Kris Kristopherson\, Guy Clark\, and Jimmie Rogers -listen to Joe Wunderle and his band.
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/joe-wunderle/
LOCATION:Drom Taberna\, 458 Queen Street West\, Old Toronto\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M5V 2A8
CATEGORIES:Nightlife,Performing Arts
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://nowtoronto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/joe-wunderle.jpg
END:VEVENT
